ses to learner data.“"}, "textbook": {"ch": "“1.Lightbown, P. M. ＆ Spada, N. (2013). How languages are learned (4th Edition). Oxford: Oxford University Press. \n2.Selected readings“", "en": "“1.Lightbown, P. M. ＆ Spada, N. (2013). How languages are learned (4th Edition). Oxford: Oxford University Press. \n2.Selected readings“"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "30", "en": "30"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討\n\n個別指導", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar", "", "Individual Instruction"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "1. Class Discussions 40％\n2. Midterm Exam 30％ \n3. Reading Reports 30％", "en": "1. Class Discussions 40％\n2. Midterm Exam 30％ \n3. Reading Reports 30％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "二上9:00-11:50", "en": "Tuesday mornings 9:00-11:50"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "Students can make an appointment if there are further questions.", "en": "個別晤談"}, "domain": {"ch": "語言學與英語教學", "en": "語言學與英語教學"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "英文閱讀解析與寫作論述", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "英語溝通與文化跨越", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "審美欣賞與多元創意", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "人文思維與社會關懷", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "組織能力與人際合作", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "English critical reading and analytical writing", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)"]}, {"competencies": "English oral communication and cultural crossing", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)"]}, {"competencies": "aesthetic appreciation and creative diversity", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(pr